'''''Death Drums Along the River''''' (yitwa '''''Sanders''''' muri [[Amerika]]) ni filimi yasohotse muri 1963 mu [[Bwongereza]] [[Ubudage|n’Ubudage]] bakoranye n’amahanga<ref>https://www.tvguide.com/movies/death-drums-along-the-river/cast/2030010397/</ref>, bakoresheje abantu bavugwa mu gitabo cya Edgar Wallace cyo mu 1911 cyitwa ''Sanders of the River'' na filime ya Zoltán Korda yo mu 1935 ishingiye ku gitabo<ref>https://www.criterionchannel.com/death-drums-along-the-river</ref>, ariko yashyizwe mu nkuru itandukanye rwose. Ifata amashusho aherereye muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika yepfo]], igaragaramo Richard Todd na Marianne Koch bayoboye itsinda ryabakinnyi b’abongereza, Abadage na Afurika yepfo<ref>https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/76144-death-drums-along-the-river</ref>. Iyi filime niyo filime yambere yerekanwe na producer w’abongereza Harry Alan Towers<ref>https://www.platekompaniet.no/dvd/death-drums-along-the-river/</ref> .

