== Uko yakozwe ==
Harry Alan Towers yakoze firime nyinshi muri [[Afurika|Afrika]] yepfo ku nkunga ya Film ya Constantin mu Budage bw’Iburengerazuba hamwe n’abakinnyi baturutse muri kiriya gihugu. <ref>https://www.themoviescene.co.uk/reviews/death-drums-along-the-river/death-drums-along-the-river.html</ref> Iyi filime yagurishijwe mu Budage bw’Iburengerazuba nka imwe mu mafilime yakunzwe cyane ya Edgar Wallace, ariko ntaho ahuriye cyane n’igitabo cya Wallace cyitwa ''Sanders of the River'', cyangwa filime zabanjirije iyi zishingiye kuri icyo gitabo, usibye izina Sanders n'ubwato<ref>https://ievenn.com/death-drums-along-the-river-1963-english/2412277/</ref>. ''Zaire'', nubwo hano ari ubwato buto bwa moteri aho kuba parike. Intambara hagati y’ibikorwa bya Wallace yasimbuwe n’inkuru isanzwe y’iperereza irimo ubwicanyi na magendu ya diyama<ref>http://www.sundayobserver.lk/2020/11/22/montage/%E2%80%98death-drums-along-river%E2%80%99</ref>. Abakoloni b'impimbano ntibahawe izina, ariko mu rwego rw'ibihe Dr Jung abaza Sanders icyo azakora igihe azahabwa ubwigenge<ref>https://www.alamy.com/stock-photo-richard-todd-death-drums-along-the-river-sanders-of-the-river-1963-30956757.html</ref> 

